temple-ruins/
│── temple_ruins.py       # main entry point
│── settings.py           # config values (tile size, colors, fps, etc.)
│── level_data.py         # level layouts & definitions
│── entities.py           # Player, Enemy, Guardian, Boulder, etc.
│── puzzles.py            # puzzle logic (switches, gates, mirrors, gears)
│── hazards.py            # moving blocks, stalactites, patrols
│── levels.py             # Level class (loads entities + puzzles + hazards)
│── utils.py              # helper functions (grid conversion, timers, etc.)
│── assets/               # (future: textures, sounds, music)
│── docs/
│   └── LEVELS.md         # detailed level-by-level documentation
│── README.md             # game overview (the one I wrote for you)

